---
import blobTrackerScript from "../scripts/blob-tracker.js?url";
---

<section class="blob-tracker">
  <h1>✨ Picos de luz conectados (tipo red)</h1>
  <p class="intro">
    Esta demo abre la cámara, detecta <strong>picos de luz</strong>, dibuja
    cuadros, los conecta como una red y te deja jugar con los parámetros para
    cambiar la estética.
  </p>

  <div class="controls">
    <div class="controls-row">
      <button id="startButton" class="primary-button"> Iniciar cámara </button>

      <button id="fullscreenButton" class="secondary-button">
        Pantalla completa
      </button>

      <label class="toggle">
        <input type="checkbox" id="invertToggle" checked />
        <span>Interior en negativo</span>
      </label>
    </div>

    <div class="sliders">
      <div class="slider-group">
        <label>
          Sensibilidad (umbral luz)
          <div class="slider-row">
            <input
              type="range"
              id="thresholdSlider"
              min="0"
              max="255"
              value="200"
            />
            <span id="thresholdValue">200</span>
          </div>
        </label>
      </div>

      <div class="slider-group">
        <label>
          Área mínima blob
          <div class="slider-row">
            <input type="range" id="minAreaSlider" min="1" max="50" value="3" />
            <span id="minAreaValue">3</span>
          </div>
        </label>
      </div>

      <div class="slider-group">
        <label>
          Área máxima blob
          <div class="slider-row">
            <input
              type="range"
              id="maxAreaSlider"
              min="20"
              max="2000"
              value="500"
            />
            <span id="maxAreaValue">500</span>
          </div>
        </label>
      </div>

      <div class="slider-group">
        <label>
          Tamaño máximo lado (px)
          <div class="slider-row">
            <input
              type="range"
              id="maxSideSlider"
              min="10"
              max="200"
              value="60"
            />
            <span id="maxSideValue">60</span>
          </div>
        </label>
      </div>

      <div class="slider-group">
        <label>
          Máximo número de blobs
          <div class="slider-row">
            <input
              type="range"
              id="maxBlobsSlider"
              min="10"
              max="300"
              value="150"
            />
            <span id="maxBlobsValue">150</span>
          </div>
        </label>
      </div>

      <div class="slider-group">
        <label>
          Conexiones por nodo
          <div class="slider-row">
            <input
              type="range"
              id="neighborsSlider"
              min="1"
              max="8"
              value="3"
            />
            <span id="neighborsValue">3</span>
          </div>
        </label>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <p id="status" class="status">Cargando OpenCV.js…</p>

  <div id="videoWrapper" class="video-wrapper">
    <!-- Vídeo oculto, solo fuente -->
    <video id="videoInput" class="hidden" autoplay playsinline muted></video>

    <!-- Canvas = resultado -->
    <canvas id="canvasOutput" class="canvas"></canvas>
  </div>

  <section class="help">
    <h2>Cómo usarlo</h2>
    <ul>
      <li>Pulsa <strong>“Iniciar cámara”</strong> y acepta el permiso.</li>
      <li>
        Ajusta la <strong>sensibilidad</strong> y los tamaños para controlar cuántos
        cuadros aparecen.
      </li>
      <li>
        Juega con <strong>“Interior en negativo”</strong> para cambiar el carácter
        de la pieza.
      </li>
      <li>
        Usa <strong>“Pantalla completa”</strong> para verlo como visual a toda pantalla.
      </li>
    </ul>
  </section>

  <script type="module" src={blobTrackerScript}></script>
</section>

<style>
  .blob-tracker {
    max-width: 960px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 2rem 1.5rem 3rem;
  }

  .blob-tracker h1 {
    font-size: 2rem;
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
  }

  .blob-tracker .intro {
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
    color: #64748b;
  }

  .controls {
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 0.75rem;
  }

  .controls-row {
    display: flex;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    gap: 0.75rem;
    align-items: center;
  }

  .sliders {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(220px, 1fr));
    gap: 0.75rem;
  }

  .slider-group label {
    font-size: 0.85rem;
    color: #cbd5f5;
    display: block;
  }

  .slider-row {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 0.5rem;
    margin-top: 0.25rem;
  }

  .slider-row input[type="range"] {
    flex: 1;
  }

  .slider-row span {
    width: 3rem;
    font-size: 0.8rem;
    text-align: right;
    color: #e5e7eb;
  }

  .primary-button,
  .secondary-button {
    display: inline-block;
    padding: 0.6rem 1.3rem;
    border-radius: 999px;
    border: 1px solid transparent;
    font-size: 0.95rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    cursor: pointer;
    transition:
      transform 0.1s ease,
      box-shadow 0.1s ease,
      filter 0.1s ease;
  }

  .primary-button {
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, #22c55e, #16a34a);
    color: #022c22;
    box-shadow: 0 10px 25px rgba(34, 197, 94, 0.4);
  }

  .primary-button:hover {
    filter: brightness(1.05);
    transform: translateY(-1px);
    box-shadow: 0 14px 30px rgba(34, 197, 94, 0.45);
  }

  .primary-button:active {
    transform: translateY(1px);
    box-shadow: 0 6px 16px rgba(34, 197, 94, 0.35);
  }

  .secondary-button {
    background: transparent;
    color: #e5e7eb;
    border-color: rgba(148, 163, 184, 0.8);
    box-shadow: 0 4px 12px rgba(15, 23, 42, 0.6);
  }

  .secondary-button:hover {
    filter: brightness(1.1);
    transform: translateY(-1px);
    box-shadow: 0 8px 18px rgba(15, 23, 42, 0.8);
  }

  .secondary-button:active {
    transform: translateY(1px);
    box-shadow: 0 3px 10px rgba(15, 23, 42, 0.7);
  }

  .toggle {
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 0.4rem;
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    color: #cbd5f5;
  }

  .toggle input {
    accent-color: #22c55e;
  }

  .status {
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    color: #9ca3af;
  }

  .video-wrapper {
    position: relative;
    width: 100%;
    border-radius: 1rem;
    overflow: hidden;
    background: #020617;
    border: 1px solid rgba(148, 163, 184, 0.3);
  }

  .canvas {
    display: block;
    width: 100%;
    height: auto;
  }

  .hidden {
    display: none;
  }

  .help {
    margin-top: 2rem;
    background: rgba(15, 23, 42, 0.9);
    border-radius: 1rem;
    padding: 1.25rem 1.5rem;
    border: 1px solid rgba(148, 163, 184, 0.4);
    color: #e5e7eb;
  }

  .help h2 {
    margin-top: 0;
    font-size: 1.1rem;
    margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
  }

  .help ul {
    margin: 0;
    padding-left: 1.25rem;
    font-size: 0.95rem;
  }

  .help li + li {
    margin-top: 0.35rem;
  }

  /* Wrapper ocupa toda la pantalla en fullscreen */
  #videoWrapper:fullscreen,
  #videoWrapper:-webkit-full-screen {
    width: 100vw;
    height: 100vh;
    max-width: none;
    max-height: none;
    border-radius: 0;
    border: none;

    display: flex;
    justify-content: center;
    align-items: center;
    background: #000; /* negro puro para que las bandas se vean bien */
  }

  /* El canvas escala manteniendo proporción */
  #videoWrapper:fullscreen .canvas,
  #videoWrapper:-webkit-full-screen .canvas {
    width: 100%;
    height: auto;
    max-height: 100%;
    display: block;
  }
</style>
